Class CustomWidthArray

java.lang.Object
edu.berkeley.nlp.lm.array.CustomWidthArray
All Implemented Interfaces:

public final class CustomWidthArray extends Object implements Serializable
An array with a custom word "width" in bits. Borrows heavily from Sux4J (http://sux.dsi.unimi.it/)
